<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">I am a level 56 enchanter.  I have recently maxed out my INT and CHA status to 255 (with self buffs).  I am now looking to add to my HPs.  Is it better to pursue additional HPs through items with STA buffs or items with HP adders.
<br />

<br />
Any advice on the matter would be greatly appreciated.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
