<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">As I recall, at level 65, 1 STA = 2.5 HPs.  My guild is farming the elementals now (yes, I know it is not end-game) and I have nowhere near 300 STA (my current cap).  From level 56 to 65, STA items will get you a small (very small) bonus every level.
<br />

<br />
Use Magelo and play around with different items.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
