<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">In general, I would say HPs, because there's a cap on stamina, and no cap on HPs.  
<br />

<br />
The real answer though is probably "both"
<br />

<br />
If in doubt, toy with magelo and find out which item gives you more HPs - but remember that if you're around a shaman, beastlord, or warrior with ornate pants often, your stamina cap is effectively lower because you'll be able to count on having a buff to cap it off.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
