<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Don't make the mistake of saying, "I'll get Stamina because it will eventually be more useful when I get ND3."  This isn't true.  Straight HP is increased with ND3 as well, not just the indirect HP you get from Stamina.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
