<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">It really depends on an item, lets take it a bit far.
<br />

<br />
1 item has 250hp and 5sta
<br />
1 item has 5hp and 150sta
<br />

<br />
Now you could say that the 150 STA item is better because it has such a large increase in STA over the other item. They pretty much equal each other out, except if you happen to cap you STA with the 150 item.
<br />
In the long run the 250hp item will have been of more value because the 150sta will take you over your cap when you start getting better and better gear with more STA on it, eventually it will only really be worth 5hp.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
