<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Remember that you expect to change armor.  Some things might be important now, but not as much when you get to the STA cap.  Decide which is best for you RIGHT NOW, then worry about upgrading later.
<br />

<br />
In my opinion, it is bad to think, "I won't get that now, since I'll probably be in TIME in 6 months and can then get better."  I've had items that lasted less than a week before I upgraded.  I was happy for the first one, and happy for the second, and never gave it a thought.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
